\"_blank\">https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/8519-3/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Pelosi Statement in Support of Hong Kong Protestors</strong><br />\nAUGUST 6, 2019<br />\n<br />\nSan Francisco &ndash; Speaker Nancy Pelosi issued this statement in support of the courageous pro-democracy protestors in Hong Kong:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;As they have all summer, today the people of Hong Kong are sending a stirring message to the world: the dreams of freedom, justice and democracy can never be extinguished by injustice and intimidation.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The extraordinary outpouring of courage from the people of Hong Kong stands in stark contrast to a cowardly government that refuses to respect the rule of law or live up to the &lsquo;one country, two systems&rsquo; framework which was guaranteed more than two decades ago.  The people of Hong Kong deserve the true autonomy that was promised, with the full rights guaranteed by the Hong Kong Basic Law and international agreements.  The Legislative Council must finally take long-overdue measures to meet the legitimate democratic aspirations of the Hong Kong people &ndash; starting with completely and immediately withdrawing the widely-repudiated extradition bill.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Democrats and Republicans in Congress stand united with the people of Hong Kong in demanding the hopeful, free and democratic future that is their right.  We reiterate the call of the Tom Lantos Human Rights Commission Co-Chairs Congressman Jim McGovern and Congressman Chris Smith to the Trump Administration to suspend future sales of munitions and crowd control equipment to the Hong Kong police force.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When we return to Washington, the bipartisan, bicameral Congress will begin our work to advance the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, and fight to preserve democratic freedoms and the rule of law in Hong Kong.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"46883b514fc1f129aad1498924bcdfd76d7e2cb8","tid":1424603,"uid":284100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"如果喺真 啲黑警真喺好大功勞"},{"pid":"37f7ff8cb3228680dfc99d3f7c2f28675b1a4942","tid":1424603,"uid":239469,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"請問有冇專業人士識搞？<br />\n楊衛隆話最好搵事主直接搞，不要由男人搞"},{"pid":"acd67521613ed64753a869272dae935857b7c5ac","tid":1424603,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"a2e09e852281dd04333d810bbdf35d94ec49e08d","tid":1424603,"uid":77416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"post 埋之前果d女仔俾警察撳落地既相<br />\n之前旺角清場好似有張相係咁<br />\n個女仔浄係拎部手機都俾人撳抵"},{"pid":"4943da990a9049f0d2650d6c9e22354b2cca5180","tid":1424603,"uid":241567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:22:25.000Z","msg":"文宣組靠你地喇 而家係你地主場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfd5874189e3a0ae31498e058ab208a48aee7de","tid":1424603,"uid":239469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AzhaoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AzhaoP.jpg&h=b3aeb0fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2020574748893174686f95b6d920446f09acc27b","tid":1424603,"uid":239469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"有冇絲打幫手？"},{"pid":"375c480624f892d3ed1a777cb0c6bd7e0f6507fd","tid":1424603,"uid":261332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"點都好，總之千萬唔好比何式凝之流插手。"},{"pid":"af579cd0f5c8f93bc477679d397ac386678108dd","tid":1424603,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s